### {202}{}{I'm counting on your loyalty. Let me give you a recommendation. According to my information, the tinkerers were accountable to an influential organization called the Brotherhood of Steel. It is this organization that is responsible for the development of slavery in Sonora. You should find a way to eliminate the Brotherhood's main base to reduce further risks to the Villa.}
{202}{}{我指望你的忠诚。让我给你推荐一下。根据我的信息，修补工们对一个名为钢铁兄弟会的有影响力的组织负责。正是这个组织对索诺拉奴隶制的发展负有责任。你应该找到一种方法来消除兄弟会的主要基地，以减少别墅的进一步风险。}
